msg":"感覺連登/香港人需要正能量<br />\n希望呢個post帶到比大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8411f03d1270af06c37ebdebc60804fea8e4c125","tid":1744154,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:45:10.000Z","msg":"早排都好頹,覺得好多手足比人拉/受傷,自己都有啲事情<br />\n但係聽完天琦講 革命唔會係一時三刻嘅事 又有返精神<br />\n光復香港仲有好長嘅路先走到,唔可以咁易放棄,天琦仲等緊我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f19ec58faf2aebb659a79a44106760416e7c90","tid":1744154,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:49:27.000Z","msg":"其實我諗 會唔會拉晒勇武入去坐,光復香港反而更易有出路<br />\n勇武入左去同天琦會合,成立秘密組織,十年後出返黎正式落力搞革命<br />\n入得去坐嘅人,都證明左係真勇武,有做地下組織嘅資格。"},{"pid":"32afbbc6a76f000d8f46fc89aaa4a19ab500a877","tid":1744154,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9f19ec58faf2aebb659a79a44106760416e7c90","tid":1744154,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:49:27.000Z","msg":"其實我諗 會唔會拉晒勇武入去坐,光復香港反而更易有出路<br />\n勇武入左去同天琦會合,成立秘密組織,十年後出返黎正式落力搞革命<br />\n入得去坐嘅人,都證明左係真勇武,有做地下組織嘅資格。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:51:21.000Z","msg":"認真討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣諗嘅話聽到義士要入獄都好過啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8fd928fc0205717b0b89c80b0025c527e24341","tid":1744154,"uid":557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:59:16.000Z","msg":"加油 , 幫推"},{"pid":"db44f7a2a70bdd66fb8e9c74865866178919f0ba","tid":1744154,"uid":192049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ddfe325baf87b859dd557e943fa7838dff7ce6b","tid":1744154,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4929907c630b8b4ea1023b2dd2151d3d9a55238f","tid":1744154,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:35:15.000Z","msg":"發覺係咪越黎越少